name: Jimmy Kimmel
summary: Following the 2016 US presidential election, late-night talk show host Jimmy Kimmel expressed his emotional distress in his opening monologue. Kimmel was visibly upset, choking up and fighting back tears as he discussed the election results and President-elect Donald Trump's victory. He referred to it as a "terrible night," comparing Trump to Emperor Palpatine from the "Star Wars" franchise and suggesting that the outcome was favorable for Russian President Vladimir Putin and the spread of preventable diseases like polio. Kimmel expressed his deep concern and disappointment, questioning the future of the country and its values.
